      "text": "\nOn [[Xp At Arinc]], We're working in MFC, a notoriously difficult environment to refactor/clean/test. After mucking around with inadequate testing facilities for a while, we came up with two approaches that seem to be making all the difference.  ",
      "id": "8a4bd0474d191ae6269cbf0300b7b029"
